    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It's mainly to make it clear that a container is used for an InstantSearch widget. With `id` we don't know if it's used for styling, JavaScript interactions, etc.\r\n\r\nIt's not super important but I'm trying different patterns while building this demo.\r\n\r\nBesides, we're becoming a `data-driven` company... haha",
